{"tid":2310198,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】估計香港140萬人受感染 袁國勇促斬斷本地傳染鏈","createTime":"2020-12-03T05:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T14:54:33.000Z","uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0d0ab0c9a0c07a2282f1636865bfb1ca43ae929b","tid":2310198,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/none/6e1b3043ad25923db710f4d62562fb93/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200206/_2020020608572925857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fnone%2F6e1b3043ad25923db710f4d62562fb93%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200206%2F_2020020608572925857.jpg&h=3a4c775b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大微生物系講座教授袁國勇今日指，隨著本地傳染鏈已開始，目前最重要是將傳染鏈斬斷。而對於本港的最終感染人數，袁國勇表示，估計數字仍然保持在140萬人。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇早上在一電台節目上表示，香港已出現本地確診個案，顯示本地傳染鏈已開始，擔心會出現社區爆發。<br />\n<br />\n他認為目前首要斬斷傳染鏈，一是不要再有內地個案輸入，二是在港採取所有可行措施，將人傳人的風險減至最低。他促請政府確保不會出現大規模本地傳染，否則即使不封關，外國也會對香港封關。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇一再提醒必需做好衛生措施，包括佩戴口罩和消毒家居。沒戴口罩的市民，便應與人保持6個階磚的距離，和應盡量避免與人接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1695175/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%BC%B0%E8%A8%88%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF140%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E4%BF%83%E6%96%AC%E6%96%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%82%B3%E6%9F%93%E9%8F%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1695175%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25BC%25B0%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF140%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593-%25E8%25A2%2581%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258B%2587%25E4%25BF%2583%25E6%2596%25AC%25E6%2596%25B7%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2582%25B3%25E6%259F%2593%25E9%258F%2588&d=tqH%2BXDs9hgzl%2F07